      <madsrdf:definitionNote xml:lang="en">The Media Types Scheme is derived from a controlled list of values reflecting the general type of intermediation device required to view, play, run, etc., the content of a resource, which is principally used in RDA cataloging.</madsrdf:definitionNote>
